00:41.361 --> 00:46.141
And I learned that economists measure everything in tangible units of production...

00:46.491 --> 00:50.806
...and consumption as if each of those tangible units is exactly the same.

00:51.808 --> 00:52.717
They aren't the same.

00:53.534 --> 00:55.249
In fact, as leaders, what we need to learn...

00:55.644 --> 00:59.681
...is that we can actually influence the quality of that unit of production...

01:00.176 --> 01:03.728
